SQL_STMT_U.val: select DCMO_YEAR DCMO_YEAR, DCMO_MONTH DCMO_MONTH, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTBEFOREDUEDATE) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_BEFORE, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTAFTDUEDAT30) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_30, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTAFTDUEDAT60) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_60, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTAFTDUEDAT90) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_90, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTAFTDUEDAT120) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_120, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTAFTDUEDATG120) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_G120, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_PARTPAYMENT, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES) as decimal(13,2)) TEMP_AMOUNT_PAIDDISPUTES, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDNINVBEFDUEDATE) as decimal(9,0)) TEMP_INVOICES_BEFORE, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDNINVAFTDUEDATE30) as decimal(9,0)) TEMP_INVOICES_30, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDNINVAFTDUEDATE60) as decimal(9,0)) TEMP_INVOICES_60, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDNINVAFTDUEDATE90) as decimal(9,0)) TEMP_INVOICES_90, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDNINVAFTDUEDATE120) as decimal(9,0)) TEMP_INVOICES_120, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDNINVAFTDUEDATEG120) as decimal(9,0)) TEMP_INVOICES_G120, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTINVDATE) as decimal (17,2)) TEMP_AVERAGE_INVDATE_1, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM) as decimal (13,2)) TEMP_AVERAGE_INVDATE_2, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDUEDATE) as decimal (17,2)) TEMP_AVERAGE_DUEDATE_1, cast(sum (DCMO_PAIDAMOUNT - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTDISPUTES - DCMO_PAIDAMOUNTPARTIALPAYM) as decimal (13,2)) TEMP_AVERAGE_DUEDATE_2 from :1/DCMO :6 join :1/DEBC on :3 :2 where DCMO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and DCMO_CURRENCY = ':4' and :5 group by DCMO_YEAR , DCMO_MONTH order by DCMO_YEAR desc, DCMO_MONTH desc for fetch only
